-- V8: More sample submissions for a fuller demo list, including a FAILED-pipeline case.
-- Adds one additional submission per status and mixes JSON_BLOB (LOAN_APPLICATION) with
-- KEY_VALUE (ACCOUNT_OPENING) storage. The failed run mirrors SubmissionPipelineService behaviour:
